{
  "meta": {
    "is_partial": true,
    "description": "답글 섹션 내용. 표시 조건(if)은 호출부(types/basic/show.json)에서 제어."
  },
  "comment": "답글 섹션 내용",
  "type": "basic",
  "name": "Div",
  "props": {
    "className": "card bg-base-100 shadow-sm"
  },
  "children": [
    {
      "comment": "답글 헤더",
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "props": {
        "className": "px-6 pt-6 pb-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700"
      },
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "H3",
          "props": {
            "className": "text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white flex items-center gap-2"
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "composite",
              "name": "Icon",
              "props": {
                "name": "comments",
                "size": "md",
                "className": "text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400"
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Span",
              "text": "$t:board.posts.detail.replies_title|count={{(post?.data?.replies ?? []).length}}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "comment": "답글 목록",
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "iteration": {
        "source": "{{post?.data?.replies ?? []}}",
        "item_var": "reply",
        "index_var": "replyIndex"
      },
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "props": {
            "className": "border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 px-6 py-4"
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "comment": "1줄: 제목 (클릭 가능)",
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Div",
              "props": {
                "className": "flex items-center gap-1 mb-2"
              },
              "children": [
                {
                  "comment": "비밀글 아이콘",
                  "type": "composite",
                  "name": "Icon",
                  "if": "{{reply?.is_secret}}",
                  "props": {
                    "name": "lock",
                    "size": "sm",
                    "className": "text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "comment": "블라인드 아이콘",
                  "type": "composite",
                  "name": "Icon",
                  "if": "{{reply?.status === 'blinded'}}",
                  "props": {
                    "name": "eye-slash",
                    "size": "sm",
                    "className": "text-orange-500 dark:text-orange-400 flex-shrink-0"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "comment": "제목 (클릭 시 해당 답글로 이동)",
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "A",
                  "props": {
                    "href": "/board/{{route.slug}}/{{reply.id}}",
                    "className": "text-lg font-bold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline"
                  },
                  "text": "{{reply?.title ?? ''}}"
                },
                {
                  "comment": "삭제됨 배지",
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Span",
                  "if": "{{reply?.deleted_at}}",
                  "props": {
                    "className": "inline-flex items-center px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs font-medium bg-red-100 text-red-700 dark:bg-red-900/30 dark:text-red-300 flex-shrink-0"
                  },
                  "text": "$t:board.post.deleted_badge"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "comment": "2줄: 아바타 + 작성자 + 날짜 + 조회수/댓글수",
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Div",
              "props": {
                "className": "flex items-center justify-between pb-2 mb-2 border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700"
              },
              "children": [
                {
                  "comment": "왼쪽: 아바타 + 작성자 정보",
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Div",
                  "props": {
                    "className": "flex items-center gap-2"
                  },
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "composite",
                      "name": "Avatar",
                      "props": {
                        "author": "{{reply?.author}}",
                        "size": "sm"
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "composite",
                      "name": "UserInfo",
                      "props": {
                        "author": "{{reply?.author}}",
                        "layout": "horizontal"
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "comment": "오른쪽: 작성일/조회수/댓글수",
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Div",
                  "props": {
                    "className": "flex items-center gap-3 text-xs text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500"
                  },
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "comment": "작성일",
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Span",
                      "props": {
                        "title": "{{reply?.created_at ?? ''}}"
                      },
                      "text": "{{reply?.created_at_formatted ?? ''}}"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Span",
                      "if": "{{post?.data?.board?.show_view_count !== false && reply?.view_count !== undefined}}",
                      "props": {
                        "className": "flex items-center gap-1"
                      },
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "composite",
                          "name": "Icon",
                          "props": {
                            "name": "eye",
                            "size": "xs"
                          }
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "basic",
                          "name": "Span",
                          "text": "{{reply.view_count}}"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Span",
                      "if": "{{reply?.comment_count !== undefined && reply?.comment_count > 0}}",
                      "props": {
                        "className": "flex items-center gap-1"
                      },
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "composite",
                          "name": "Icon",
                          "props": {
                            "name": "message-square",
                            "size": "xs"
                          }
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "basic",
                          "name": "Span",
                          "text": "{{reply.comment_count}}"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "comment": "3줄: 내용 미리보기 (토글로 접기/펼치기)",
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Div",
              "props": {
                "className": "text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-2 {{_local?.expandedReplyId === reply?.id ? '' : 'line-clamp-2'}}"
              },
              "children": [
                {
                  "comment": "블라인드 처리된 경우",
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Span",
                  "if": "{{reply?.status === 'blinded'}}",
                  "props": {
                    "className": "italic text-orange-500 dark:text-orange-400"
                  },
                  "text": "$t:board.blinded_post"
                },
                {
                  "comment": "비밀글 안내",
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Span",
                  "if": "{{reply?.status !== 'blinded' && reply?.is_secret}}",
                  "props": {
                    "className": "italic text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
                  },
                  "text": "$t:board.posts.detail.reply_secret_content"
                },
                {
                  "comment": "일반 글 내용",
                  "type": "composite",
                  "name": "HtmlContent",
                  "if": "{{reply?.status !== 'blinded' && !reply?.is_secret}}",
                  "props": {
                    "content": "{{reply?.content ?? ''}}",
                    "isHtml": "{{(reply?.content_mode ?? 'text') === 'html'}}",
                    "className": "prose-sm dark:prose-invert max-w-none {{_local?.expandedReplyId === reply?.id ? '' : '[&_img]:hidden [&_table]:hidden'}}"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "comment": "4줄: 더보기/접기 토글 버튼 (테두리 없음) - 200자 이상이고 블라인드 아닌 경우만 표시",
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Div",
              "if": "{{reply?.status !== 'blinded' && !reply?.is_secret && (reply?.content ?? '').length > 200}}",
              "props": {
                "className": "flex justify-start"
              },
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Button",
                  "props": {
                    "className": "text-sm text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-400 dark:hover:text-gray-200 bg-transparent border-0 p-0 cursor-pointer flex items-center gap-1"
                  },
                  "actions": [
                    {
                      "type": "click",
                      "handler": "setState",
                      "params": {
                        "target": "local",
                        "expandedReplyId": "{{_local?.expandedReplyId === reply?.id ? null : reply?.id}}"
                      }
                    }
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "composite",
                      "name": "Icon",
                      "props": {
                        "name": "{{_local?.expandedReplyId === reply?.id ? 'chevron-up' : 'chevron-down'}}",
                        "size": "sm"
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Span",
                      "text": "{{_local?.expandedReplyId === reply?.id ? '$t:board.show_less' : '$t:board.show_more'}}"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
